In the town of Valparaiso in Chile, a downhill mountain bike competition has
been taking place for the last 10 years; the [Valparaíso Cerro Abajo
cup](http://www.valparaisocerroabajo.cl/). What makes it different from many
other downhill races is the location: this race takes place in the city
streets and sidewalks.

[![](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/800px-
Sarajevo_urban_downhill_race-375x281.jpg)](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2011/03/800px-Sarajevo_urban_downhill_race.jpg)[Sarajevo
Downhill
